          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Expect to spend over $1 million for any Ferrari Spyder (convertible) from the era. Prices often extend deep into seven figures. True open top Ford GT’s number in the single digits. The most recent public sale netted $7,650,000 at ",
